item.title: WNBA Star Angel Reese Makes Feature Film Debut With Cameo in Netflix Nuclear Disaster Thriller
item.description: The basketball phenom is in good company: Reese stars as herself in Kathryn Bigelow’s ‘A House of Dynamite’ in a scene with Idris Elba as the president of the United States.
